description: Modelling agent Jean-Luc Brunel faces accusations of rape and human trafficking, French media say.
title: Jeffrey Epstein ex-associate Jean-Luc Brunel held over sex crime claims
title_page: Jeffrey Epstein ex-associate Jean-Luc Brunel held over sex crime claims - BBC News
maintext: Last year, French prosecutors opened an inquiry into rape and sexual assault allegations against Epstein to focus on potential crimes committed against French victims and on suspects who are French citizens, they said at the time.
